<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT13">
<l>irumpaṉaṉ ṟuṇṭa nīrum pōtaruṅ koḷka veṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>arumpiṇi pāva mellā makaṉṟaṉa veṉṉai viṭṭu</l>
<l>curumpamar cōlai cūḻnta varaṅkamā kōyil koṇṭa</l>
<l>karumpiṉaik kaṇṭu koṇṭeṉ kaṇṇiṇai kaḷikku māṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Water consumed [by] an iron burning disappears; Grasp [that]!</l>
<l>[Thus] all of my harsh suffering and sins have fled, leaving me.</l>
<l>Seeing for myself the Sugarcane who has taken as [his] great temple Araṅkam,</l>
<l>Surrounded by groves [where] bees settle, ah, the way [it] intoxicates both my eyes!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
